race.description: Associated Cold Tread Tyres Mdn Plate
race.comment: JENNI BASSETT (10) is a three-start maiden who could only manage to finish fourth after being in the firing line on the corner at her latest appearance over 1600m at Bendigo. Rates highly in this field and can turn things around. CONVAAYA (5) is a talented gelding who tackled tougher grade last time, finishing 13 lengths behind Freedom Flame over 1800m in the LR Hill Smith Stakes at Morphettville. Blinkers go on and among the leading chances. MOZZONI (11) ran a better race second time out to finish fifth over 1400m at Nowra. Don't underestimate. I BELIEVE I BELONG (9) started at lengthy odds on debut last start and reflected that lack of market confidence when finishing back in eighth over 1300m at Echuca. Fitter and can only be improved here.
